{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value other than ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","title":"targetCoordinate","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"kind":"symbol","abst